Cover Letter Tips

To:
1. Dear Name/Hiring Manager (Check LinkedIn)
2. Dear Hiring Manager
3. Dear [Company Name]

Body:
Role: 			   Why at company -> Problems trying to solve w/ data -> express interest
Qualifications:    Core competencies w/ data science
Capstone Project:  Proof, link, completed
Closing Statement: Best Regards

Testing Resume:
Many companies have filter systems, use below links to test your resume, resume should be 75-80% relevancy
Jobscan.co
Resunate.com

Networking opportunities are always first and then job applications